        Inclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Adults over 18 years of age.&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Undergoing anesthesia-assisted endoscopic procedures.&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Able to give appropriate consent to the study or have an appropriate representative to&#xD;
             do so.&#xD;
&#xD;
        Exclusion Criteria:&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Pregnancy.&#xD;
&#xD;
          -  Physical deformity, wound, or dressing preventing placement of a wearable device on&#xD;
